Package net.aifusion.metamodel

Enum DataType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<DataType>
net.aifusion.metamodel.DataType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DataType>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum DataType
extends java.lang.Enum<DataType>
This enum contains all known CIM data types, as well as commonly used methods for manipulating them

Sharad Singhal
